<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        @keyframes floatComet {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg);
                opacity: 0.3;
            }

            50% {
                transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(10deg);
                opacity: 1;
            }

            100% {
                transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg);
                opacity: 0.3;
            }
        }

        @keyframes glow {
            0% {
                box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(100, 200, 255, 0.2);
            }

            50% {
                box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(100, 200, 255, 0.4);
            }

            100% {
                box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(100, 200, 255, 0.2);
            }
        }

        .card {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #151a3c, #0e1230);
            border: 1px solid #2a2f4d;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            animation: glow 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .comet {
            position: absolute;
            top: -30px;
            right: -30px;
            width: 80px;
            animation: floatComet 6s ease-in-out infinite;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .stars {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/stardust.png');
            opacity: 0.1;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        body{
        background-color: #0b0f2a;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 40px;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        color: #ffffff;
        overflow: hidden;}
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="stars"></div>

    <div class="card" style="position: relative; z-index: 1;">
        <img src="src/img/logocaleCJ.png" alt="CometJet Logo"
            style="width: 200px; display: block; margin: 0 auto 20px;" />


        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">Dear <strong>
                <%= name %>
            </strong>,</p>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
            Thank you for submitting your application to <strong>CometJet Virtual Airlines</strong>. We‚Äôre happy to
            confirm that we have successfully received your application.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
            Our recruitment team will review your submission shortly. The approval process usually takes just a few
            hours, but please allow up to 5 days in rare cases.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
            You will be notified via email as soon as your application has been reviewed.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
            If you have any questions in the meantime, feel free to reach out to us via <strong>Discord</strong> or
            email.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 18px; text-align: center; color: #6ecbff; margin-top: 30px;">
            Welcome aboard ‚Äì and thank you for choosing CometJet! üõ∞Ô∏è
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #aaa; margin-top: 40px;">
            Best regards,<br>
            <strong>CometJet Team</strong>
        </p>

        <img class="comet" src="src/img/kometka.png" alt="Comet">
    </div>
    </body>

</html>
